{"tid":2202972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國更新對中國及香港的旅遊警示","createTime":"2020-09-15T04:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T09:11:44.000Z","uid":241764,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d5020e7bf027523ea785a0aa67435f4a7857ba","tid":2202972,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"至於香港，旅遊建議則由原本第二級的「提高警覺」，上調至第三級「重新考慮是否前往」，指香港的交通和商業活動已大致恢復正常，但提醒美國公民，香港在七月一日實施港區國安法，參與示威或其他活動可能會被當局視為觸犯分裂、顛覆和恐怖活動，或勾結外國勢力等刑事罪行，強烈呼籲美國公民注意周邊情況，避免到有示威的地區。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405592&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=23b26674\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405592&h=3a0c2f6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405592</a>"},{"pid":"98a6dcd9bfad0874256a566057a0c8011067069f","tid":2202972,"uid":35814,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"旅遊氣泡（爆破）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d936d372d9333f7a818938161e964af6ed45571","tid":2202972,"uid":8196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a6dcd9bfad0874256a566057a0c8011067069f","tid":2202972,"uid":35814,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"旅遊氣泡（爆破）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0893bacb4bc07ed22c6817c5499fc2271f9196","ti